# Project Name
Amr Media Generator & Regenerated AMR Project Consolidation

## Overview
The root folder **D:\All DATA\claude project** contains multiple overlapping copies of a media‑generation application (Flask server, smart agents, backup system, etc.) as well as auxiliary assets and duplicate backup archives. The goal is to produce a unified, well‑structured codebase with clear documentation, remove orphaned/duplicate files, and define a clean architecture for future development.

## Detected Projects
| Detected Path | Description |
|---|---|
| `generat photo and video/` | Primary implementation of the Amr Media Generator (v1.0) with Flask API, smart agents, backup manager, UI templates, and built executable.
| `generat photo and video - Copy (2)/` | Exact duplicate of the above project (likely an accidental copy). Contains identical source files and compiled artifacts.
| `regenerat project amr/` | A second, more extensive copy of the same application with additional scripts (`full_pipeline.py`, `creative_engine.py`, `streamlit_app.py`, etc.). Appears to be a later iteration or experimental branch.

## Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Python 3.11, Flask, `smart_agent` orchestration
- **Media**: MoviePy, custom `image_engine`, `veo_generator`
- **Backup**: 7‑Zip AES‑256 encrypted `.rar` archives
- **Deployment**: PyInstaller‑generated executable
- **Versioning**: `version_manager.py` with JSON version file
- **Configuration**: JSON files under `config/`
- **UI**: HTML templates (`templates/index.html`), CSS/JS assets
- **Additional**: Streamlit app (`streamlit_app.py`) in the regenerated project

